Author: bongshelter
Text: I always feel tired and bloated no matter what I eat. Eating before midnight is a danger to my fitbit steps.  Somehow I start to forget that around hour 20 or so, when I start getting tempted by food.

Text: yes!!! i feel physically disgusting when i break longer fasts, and it feels hard to eat at all. broth made me nauseous the other day. wtf @our bodies
